description:
Morocco is located in the northwest corner of Africa. Thanks to its stunning landscapes, colorful cities, year-round pleasant weather, and unique cuisine, Morocco is a popular travel destination. And although the country is rapidly modernizing, it still retains much of its ancient architecture and even more of its traditional customs. In this video, well highlight 10 amazing places that you should visit in Morocco. 

10. Fez
 Recommended - Guided tour of the old town: https://www.getyourguide.com/fes-l829/fez-medina-4-hour-guided-tour-t75985/?partner_id=57UJ5GF&utm_medium=online_publisher&placement=content-middle&cmp=Fez_video
 Recommended - Palais Fes Yahya: https://www.booking.com/hotel/ma/palais-fes-yahya.en.html?aid=7936148&no_rooms=1&group_adults=2
 Fez video: https://youtu.be/aAtHlcWuOhQ

9. Essaouira & the Atlantic Coast
 Recommended - Suite Azur Hotel: https://www.booking.com/hotel/ma/suite-azur.en.html?aid=7936148&no_rooms=1&group_adults=2

8. Dades Valley
 Monkey Fingers hike info: https://worldwildhearts.hopp.to/monkey-fingers-hike

7. Chefchaouen
 Recommended - Free walking tour of Chefchaouen: https://worldwildhearts.hopp.to/chefchaouen-walking-tour
 Chefchaouen video: https://youtu.be/yRwftlFoO4Q

6. Marrakech
 Recommended - Free walking tour: https://www.freetour.com/marrakech/exploring-marrakech-old-city-secrets?referralID=ZdvRXrkURXUfA7zT&campaign=Marrakechvideo
 Recommended - Riad Spa Sindibad: https://www.booking.com/hotel/ma/riad-sindibad.en.html?aid=7936148&no_rooms=1&group_adults=2
 Video Marrakech: https://youtu.be/0NkAE4N8E1A

5. Ouzoud Waterfalls
 Recommended - Ouzoud Waterfalls day tour from Marrakech: https://www.getyourguide.com/marrakech-l208/day-trip-ouzoud-waterfalls-from-marrakech-t56037/?partner_id=57UJ5GF&utm_medium=online_publisher&placement=content-middle&cmp=Marrakech_video

4. Todra Gorge
 Todra Gorge Hike: https://worldwildhearts.hopp.to/todra-gorge-hike

3. At Ben Haddou 
 Day trip from Marrakech: https://www.getyourguide.com/marrakech-l208/private-ouarzazate-and-ait-benhaddou-day-trip-t59397/?partner_id=57UJ5GF&utm_medium=online_publisher&placement=content-middle&cmp=Morocco_video
 Recommended - Chez Brahim: https://www.booking.com/hotel/ma/chez-brahim.en.html?aid=7936148&no_rooms=1&group_adults=2

2. High Atlas Region
 Atlas 2 day trek & village stay from Marrakech: https://www.getyourguide.com/imlil-l1205/marrakech-2-day-atlas-mountains-trek-with-village-stay-t279112/?partner_id=57UJ5GF&utm_medium=online_publisher&placement=content-middle&cmp=Morocco_video
